column3: "Pulling Back from the Brink! The Formidable Reinforcements – Germa!" Transliteration: "Kishi Kaisei – Saikyō no Engun Jeruma!" (Japanese: 起死回生 最強の援軍ジェルマ!)

"An Explosive Situation! Two Emperors of the Sea Going After Luffy!" Transliteration: "Isshoku Soku Hatsu – Rufi Nerau Futari no Yonkou" (Japanese: ルフィを狙う二人の四皇)
